 have some things that I think is important when we do this. But we talk of everything about this as we go...</p><p>I look forward to hearing from you!</p><p>Thank you both again for your inspiring conversation.</p><p>Niklas</p></div><p>Hello Niklas,</p><p>It's a great idea of you to bring people together who speak the same language!</p><p>The opportunity to talk to someone in Dutch (my native language) would be very helpful i think. It's easier to say what you want to say if you don't have to search for words to use.</p><p>So i'm sorry that we don't speak the same language, but maybe we can start a thread or something to find people who do and connect them. Your idea sounds very good, so i'm in! <img src="smilies/smile.png" alt="smily"></p>
